{"id":634519,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【豆瓣】太难受了！77岁的武汉老人注册微博求助，/","date":"2020-02-06T17:44:28Z","modified":"2020-02-06T17:47:12Z","title":"【豆瓣】太难受了！77岁的武汉老人注册微博求助，第一条微博是“你好”","content":"<p>来自: 弹丸少女(だよ)2020-02-06 02:25:58</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>大晚上看到这个真的心里堵的慌，太难受了。不知道有没有鹅看到，一个武汉退休教师，77岁了！女儿感染后没被确诊住院就去世了。老伴也严重感染，外孙女跟自己也被单肺感染。</p>\n<p>因为社区求助无门，颤颤巍巍地注册了微博，发送了第一条微博“你好”！隔着屏幕能感受到老人的绝望。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634521\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏-139x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1082\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634522\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏2-2-139x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1082\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏2-2-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏2-2-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏2-2-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏2-2-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏2-2-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏2-2.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634523\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏3-2-139x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1082\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏3-2-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏3-2-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏3-2-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏3-2-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏3-2-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏3-2.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>社会虽然烂了，但是好人还是更多！发了求助信息后，很多网友接力帮老爷爷提交求助信息了，祝福他们一家能快点住院，早日康复。</p>\n<p>这个时候好恨自己没有能力帮助他们😭😭😭只能再次重申！！！</p>\n<p>狗guan biss，那些只会唱赞歌的人祝你们早日获取现世报！🎉</p>\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;</p>\n<p>2月6日上午10点更新</p>\n<p>老人的微博又更新了一条新进展，微博是他的外甥女代发的（老人是代发者的大舅，估计也是爸爸妈妈辈的人）。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>1⃣老人不需要要物质、金钱捐助，目前有太多人微博打赏了，后面会一一退还。</p>\n<p>2⃣已经尝试过提交所有求助渠道，不需要重复填报了！</p>\n<p>3⃣老人很虚弱了，无力应对多余的关心，大家不要过多打扰。如果有其他更好的办法请拨打电话027-81781773！</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634524\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏4-2-300x282.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏4-2-300x282.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/老苏4-2.jpg 758w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,38912,39707],"tags":[39648,39754]}